bilingual.source: That is why when the stars are out, they are visible.
bilingual.target: 这就是为什么星星出来时是可见的。
这个标志在夜晚是可见的。

bilingual.source: The mountain is visible from a distance.
bilingual.target: 这座山从远处是可见的。

bilingual.source: His mood changes are visible on his face.
bilingual.target: 他的情绪变化在脸上是可见的。

bilingual.source: Make sure the sign is visible from the road.
bilingual.target: 确保标志从路上是可见的。

bilingual.source: The stars are visible in the clear night sky.
bilingual.target: 星星在晴朗的夜空中是可见的。

bilingual.source: The mountain peak is visible from our hotel room.
bilingual.target: 从我们酒店的房间可以看到山峰是可见的。

bilingual.source: Through the microscope, the cell structure is visible.
bilingual.target: 通过显微镜，细胞结构是可见的。

bilingual.source: The changes in the system are not immediately visible.
bilingual.target: 系统的变化不是立即可见的。

bilingual.source: Astronomers study the stars visible in each hemisphere.
bilingual.target: 天文学家研究每个半球可见的星星。

list.abstract: 由广州于2006成立的VisibleDenim牛仔工作室，筹备了将近一年所推出的又一原创服饰品牌，产品包括圆领的全纯棉卫衣及采用超厚板材和仿木制作的眼镜系列。

yingyinNormal.en: No visible reaction. Image number two: sousaphone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无显著反应。画面2: 低音喇叭。

yingyinNormal.en: You should've let me meet you at your place. Would've been considerably less visible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 应该在你的地方见面的，这里太容易被人看到了。

yingyinNormal.en: Which is why governments usually end up taking things into their own more visible hands instead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就是为什么政府到最后通常都会用「看得到的手」进行操控。

yingyinNormal.en: I realize it couldn't be anything too visible, but I've been following everything with America Works.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道我不能明目张胆，但我一直在跟进美国就业法案的报道。

yingyinNormal.en: I think it's a little early for Mercury to be visible yet. Playing hard to get. I like that in a planet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在要看到水星还太早了点吧。玩欲擒故纵。我就喜欢这样的行星。

yingyinNormal.en: And yes my lashes are real. They're sparse, very sad. Ayway, I'm going to coat eyelashes so there's some visible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的睫毛是真的，虽然很稀少，悲剧。我要涂睫毛膏啦，这样有些睫毛就可以看得见。
